node.text: Leandre Sanders, aka The @SkateGoat: "I want to share this with you all, the film about my life. Here is the trailer filmed by @van_alpert so excited to say we he is now done with the SkateGoat movie and ready to change the world by bringing families together with love. From the time I was 11 years old till now it documents 13 years of my life, my struggle, and the evolution of my skating. LOVE YOU ALL" 🎥 @van_alpert @allday #skateboardingisfun #berrics #skategoatmovie

node.text: Its @alexmidler’s 23rd birthday today! 🥳 With all that he’s done at The Berrics (and all around the world), it’s hard to believe that he’s only 23 years old. Here’s just a taste of some of the incredible clips he’s gotten within these walls. Make sure you go wish Alex a very special Happy Birthday and be on the lookout for his #BATB12 game premiering this weekend! Happy Birthday Midler!! 🎂🎁 #skateboardingisfun #berrics

@becker_dunn gets it done in his Aftertime part 📼 “The name ‘Aftertime’ means “the time to come; the future.” And Becker is going to have a great future. This is a minute long part that’s short and sweet, but really f**king good.” Edited by @bobbybils 🎬 Filmed by @alan_hannon @eric_iwakura @alexkissinger @bobbybils @steaktage & Richie Parry

Hit the link in our bio to see Becker make his Battle At The Berrics debut against Ray Corey now playing on TheBerrics.com 📺 #skateboardingisfun #berrics

node.text: We featured @raycorey in our “Where The Hell” segment earlier this year and today, just a few short months later, he made his Battle At The Berrics debut in his game against Becker Dunn. The more skating we see from Ray, the more it’s making us ask, where the hell did this guy come from?! Hit the link in our bio to watch Ray Corey vs Becker Dunn now playing on TheBerrics.com 📺 #skateboardingisfun #berrics

node.text: It’s @kristion_sk8’s 13th birthday today! 🥳 Make sure you go wish the freshly turned teenager a very happy birthday today 🎉 In the meantime, enjoy his epic “Where The Hell” session that he filmed when he was just 12 years old 🤯 Just taking a look at what he’s done before even hitting his teenage years, it’s quite clear that he has a bright future ahead of him! 🙌 We wish you all the best! Happy Birthday Kristion!! 🎁🎂 #skateboardingisfun #berrics

node.text: But one more thing!… if a 64 man bracket wasn’t insane enough, for the first time in skate history, we're going to find out which CEOs of big name action sports beverages are actually the best at skating! Running alongside this year's BATB12, the Founder/CEO of @liquiddeath Mountain Water (@notmikecessario) is publically inviting the CEOs of @redbull, @rockstarenergy, @monsterenergy, and @mountaindew to a flatground skate battle to see who takes home the title as BATB Beverage CEO Champion! Who do you got?!👇 #skateboardingisfun #berrics

Check back for continuous updates and remember let’s keep it clean, let’s keep it lean. This is BATTLE AT THE BERRICS 12!
